## Limitations

This report is based on available data up to October 2023 and may not include the latest research findings. The rapidly evolving nature of COVID-19 research means that new evidence could emerge, potentially altering the current understanding of ivermectin's role in COVID-19 treatment. Additionally, the influence of social and political factors on public perception and use of ivermectin is complex and may not be fully captured in this report.